{"tid":734074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本豪雨成災】京都、廣島屋塌土石流　已46人死亡47人失蹤","createTime":"2018-07-08T10:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T11:28:49.000Z","uid":189160,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0565aa5a56ea9bdf985866469b860ddc4f9f26","tid":734074,"uid":189160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"3日起豪雨侵襲日本，引起許多地區發生土石流與水災，災情不斷更新。根據《朝日新聞》、日本《NHK》電視台報導，至7日下午5點左右，已造成至少46人死亡、47人失蹤。目前，日本氣象廳已對京都、兵庫縣、岡山縣、岐阜縣等地發布數十年罕見的大雨特別警報。<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前有個post係話日本去水位可以養到魚<br />\n係咪d去水位養晒雨搞到死左咁多人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a34ccf470637e5a726a503febc6af899fc54863","tid":734074,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"188ee869ff6dae2b07ec8673a6bfa28c2f647ce8","tid":734074,"uid":67840,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42338efb50d1d9266617d1f53456b75c9b94de24","tid":734074,"uid":54502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"去水位擋到泥石流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63df04a76da80881625da84bc425acccbff9b37d","tid":734074,"uid":59518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"42338efb50d1d9266617d1f53456b75c9b94de24","tid":734074,"uid":54502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"去水位擋到泥石流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"柒到冇眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbbfaae788a9ec0dce68172227389ee9e3da06f","tid":734074,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"一場暴雨睇到日本幾撚